ygData.messageBody:

now that you mention this, it seems while using the
new ui, that the female Vah Shir is very skinny.
Similar to the Iksar but more agile looking,

nonetheless, the char did not look like anything I
have seen yet.


I will check tonight.....hmmm maybe create on from
scratch to see.


Glad I am not crazy........................YET
